Package ohos.multimodalinput.event

Class KeyEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.multimodalinput.event.MultimodalEvent
      • ohos.multimodalinput.event.KeyEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequenceable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BuiltinKeyEvent, KeyBoardEvent

    public abstract class KeyEvent
extends MultimodalEvent
    Defines all key events.

    This class extends the MultimodalEvent class. It defines the keycodes and methods for various key events.

    The keycodes are as follows:

    • -1: unknown keycode, which is the default value
    • 1 to 1000: keycodes for common keys
    • 1001 to 1999: keycodes for internal key devices
    • 2000 to 3000: keycodes for external key devices (mainly external keyboards)
    • 10001 to the value specified by NOW_MAX_KEY: keycodes for vehicle keys
    Since:
    1
    See Also:
    MultimodalEvent
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.MultimodalInput#MULTIMODAL_INPUT
